69 CR 180,

1:54:28.833 --> 1:54:32.166
United States of America
v. David Dellinger et al.

1:54:42.875 --> 1:54:46.458
The law requires that before sentencing,

1:54:46.541 --> 1:54:51.458
I allow the defendant or defendants
