1:56:14.458 --> 1:56:15.375
Brief.

1:56:15.958 --> 1:56:16.833
Brief.

1:56:19.625 --> 1:56:22.958
If I do these things,
my government will look favorably on me.

1:56:23.041 --> 1:56:24.250
You understand?

1:56:25.250 --> 1:56:26.083
Yes, sir.

